meta_description: Experience the heritage and culture of Valdez, the Copper River Basin, and Prince William Sound, Alaska. Learn about Alaskan First People's, 1890s Gold Rush, Pioneering Bush Pilots, the 1964 Great Alaskan Earthquake, and 1989 Exxon Valdez Oil Spill.
collections_text: Textiles and Fiber Arts from Valdez Museum Collections
